high_descs: Go to the counter with the bread, potato and toaster on it.
Pick up the potato from the counter.
Turn left and cross the room to the sink, which has a microwave over it.
Place the potato in the microwave and cook it.
Remove the potato from the microwave, turn left, cross the room and turn right to face the garbage can.
Put the potato in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Cook the potato and throw it out.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the stove.
Pick up a potato from the counter.
Move to the microwave above the sink behind you.
Put the potato inside and heat it for a few seconds before removing it and close the door.
Move the the bin to the left of the sink at the end of the counter.
Place the potato inside the bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the bin.

high_descs: Cross the room to the counter to the right of the stove
Take the potato from the back left corner of the counter
turn around, and cross the room to the sink, then look up at the microwave
Cook the potato in the microwave for 3 seconds, and then remove it when the cooking is done.
Turn left and go to the wall, then turn right to face the trash can
Put the potato in the trash can
